- Don't capitalize first letter
- No period at the end

## Body

- Wrap at 72 characters
- Explain **what** and **why** (not **how**)
- Use bullet points for multiple changes
- Reference issues/PRs if applicable

## Examples

```
feat(core): add TimeManager singleton for time control

- Centralize all time scale management
- Support pause and multiple speed settings (1x, 2x, 4x, 8x)
- Listen to EventBus for time scale requests

Closes #123
```

```
refactor(gamestate): remove redundant time management

Remove _isPaused and _timeScale fields that duplicate TimeManager
functionality. All time state queries now delegate to TimeManager.

This improves separation of concerns and reduces state duplication.
```

## Commit Grouping

Group related changes into logical commits:
- One feature per commit when possible
- Group refactors together if they're part of the same change
- Separate bug fixes from features
- Keep configuration changes separate from code changes
